{"tid":130971,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"毒撚秒回(62)","createTime":"2017-02-22T17:58:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T18:25:50.000Z","uid":18642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"815fb5465f1293ce795bf3c6e8264f560150836a","tid":130971,"uid":18642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T17:58:50.000Z","msg":"愛我別走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\nTo 某冬<br />\n現在已夜深 難將哭聲收細<br />\n平時大男人 還強裝都枉費<br />\n努力去假裝清醒 難堪都不出聲<br />\n回憶卻未流逝</span>"},{"pid":"5175862d3305a3bee67bd3a299c661a5502b4f4b","tid":130971,"uid":18642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T17:59:58.000Z","msg":"聽講開新post會有睡意"},{"pid":"a1d630d225e06858ec645bf17aa5ec8ad1d9a896","tid":130971,"uid":18642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:00:21.000Z","msg":"新post新開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dea80794b96476a0e983864c9d60cb214388702","tid":130971,"uid":16066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:00:36.000Z","msg":"正歌<br />\n正到飛天"},{"pid":"bf124c96cbb854083302458706a7781bc430a19c","tid":130971,"uid":18642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:00:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正歌<br />\n正到飛天</blockquote><br />\nagger"},{"pid":"96ffd33b3756d94dfb388f14cea014000d8dd5dc","tid":130971,"uid":40306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:01:12.000Z","msg":"而我不知道你唱甚麼"},{"pid":"862304ff299c88b50d042f7cdd702251a21c4b72","tid":130971,"uid":3283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:01:16.000Z","msg":"我無睡意 仆街"},{"pid":"a4d9326eb5176bc81803b3b9c750231cd43f2322","tid":130971,"uid":74455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:01:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好似成個人比呢個POST consume左咁<br />\n成個二月都係度日夜mon住個po<br />\n起身到訓果刻都係<br />\n毒撚秒回呢個標題根本係為我而設<br />\n<br />\n我人生一直係做緊等人回果位<br />\n讀書果陣唔知係咪聲音問題,好多時都冇人聽到我就算我係佢地側跟<br />\nWhatsapp每次彈msg都比我見到我會即刻有衝動去秒回<br />\n我明佢地有時可能忙而秒回唔到<br />\n但感覺好似我有比其他人多雙倍既時間去同人傾計咁<br />\n有時等左一日兩日佢地先答果種心情好似企係間房用咪講野但冇人理你咁<br />\n<br />\n過左咁耐有時我會心裡作祟,就算有能力秒回都好都特登等下先應佢<br />\n叫做拎番個revenge<br />\n但冇耐就發覺自己根本冇leverage去嬲佢地,<br />\n現實係人地根本已經wfc你.<br />\n<br />\n我唔止一次因為比人wfc而freakout左<br />\n同現實,同網友都試過<br />\n係三人group入面比佢地兜口兜面skip左我果句跟住問另一個人既問題, 係我眼中係比人wfc既最高境界.<br />\n姐係好似你面同面問a君野<br />\n但a君當你透明,同你背後既b君講野一樣咁.<br />\n如果呢個世界有超能力, 我既超能力係對人有雙倍既attention<br />\n點解其他人比人忽略好似冇咩感覺<br />\n定係佢地未被人忽略過?我真係答唔到<br />\n係我既世界其他人好似用書信一樣既速度溝通咁<br />\n我好驚連秒回PO入面既我都比人wfc左<br />\n其實我暗地裡係一個負能樣<br />\n打呢篇千字文叫春都只係好驚再有日冇人再理我<br />\nIn case any of you guys care</blockquote><br />\n有我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d27f079e17379505ba4dea10f1d4d17ff940da","tid":130971,"uid":3283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:01:35.000Z","msg":"有啲想繼續講"},{"pid":"1bb76892d13b5d7b169ab60c7368dfba9a249d2e","tid":130971,"uid":74455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲想繼續講</blockquote><br />\n講緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩同人講完電話"},{"pid":"df080f2cea46e0ba6d9e5a6815b71a590c0b2754","tid":130971,"uid":18642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:02:11.000Z","msg":"屌你又推返上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19689f23cc345505a3f7d016e6c3e17581d68332","tid":130971,"uid":18642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:02:44.000Z","msg":"佢唔想見返篇文呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc69e33f80ea676ac8017b9740cf433394da230","tid":130971,"uid":40306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply